{{Top|leg}}
The designation '''TST-S''' referred to a pair of [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class T-4a shuttles]] owned and operated by the [[Twin Suns Transport Services/Legends|Twin Suns Transport Services]] run by the [[Azzameen family]]. They were present on the [[Twin Suns Station (space station)|Twin Sun Station]] when the [[Viraxo]] and their allies from the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] attacked the Azzameen family assets. Both shuttles evacuated some of the crew from the platform before it was attacked, and they managed to escape thanks to the help of [[Ace/Legends|Ace]] and [[Aeron Azzameen]], who were recovering station supplies.

